            "review_text": "a basic guide to playing the Byzantine faction\n\n1) avoid fighting on two fronts\n\n2) build a lot of ships\n\n3) you have amazing units, but you can only build most of them in castles\n\n4) it's good to create forts\n\n5) It's good to increase your generals' traits so you can tax a settlement more\n\nthese are just some basics"
