            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.4779411852359772,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "best medieval strategy game out there. Factions are amazing from the Ottomans and elite Janissaries to the aggressive ruthless Mongols with 80% of their army being Turks... Subutai what the hell (proceeds to throat sing)! Unfortunately Timurids cannot be played here which is a big miss - which could pave way for Babur' Mughal Empire in India. Only thing I dislike is how stupid AI can be for route decision which makes sense given the game's age. The best thing about this game is just turkifying the whole world and destroying all Catholic/Orthodox states. And yes, No Constantinople. Just İstanbul!"
